section.section:
This section does not apply to policies:
issued to exempt commercial policyholders, as defined in § 11-206(j) of this article; or
for which the renewal policy premium is:

text.section:
The requirements of this section do not apply to the extent that the premium increase results from:
an increase in the units of exposure;
the application of an experience rating plan;
the application of a retrospective rating plan;
a change made by the insured that increases the insurer's exposure; or
an audit of the insured.
